{"about_the_game":"You play as a young man dealing with the aftermath of your father's death. After the funeral, you receive an invite to return to your childhood home to visit your mother's best friend, Monica and her two daughters, whom you grew up with. It has been several years since you've seen them, so the game centers around your quest to re-build these old relationships, forge new ones and deal with everything life has to throw at you, including the fallout from your deceased father's will.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287710/extras/mon_kat_steam_sheet.png?t=1732040666\" /><br>In addition to the three ladies you're staying with, there'll be plenty of other characters in play (friends, foes, neighbors, stalkers and many more) and a mystery to solve, as you realize that someone is secretly trying to manipulate your decisions. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287710/extras/jen_zar_steam_sheet.png?t=1732040666\" /><br><strong>&quot;Where the Heart is&quot;</strong> is a choice-driven adult Visual Novel (VN) with thousands of still images in addition to fully animated, multi-POV lewd scenes. There are eleven women to pursue in season 1 (with additions in subsequent seasons), countless decisions to make (ALL of which matter)  and realistic characters and dialog, including lots of humor.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287710/extras/deb_lil_steam_sheet.png?t=1732040666\" /><br>Some characters will be easier/harder to &quot;crack&quot; and some relationships will be a slow-burn romance (or corruption) while others will be a quick passionate affair (or rejection).  Will you focus on one girl or try to pursue as many as possible?  Each girl in the game has their own distinct personality and back-story and they will dynamically react to your previous decisions and also